reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This item is very sturdy which was unexpected. I figured it would be like all the others I’ve ordered! It was super easy to put together and holds so much! I got it for my shoes and the pink matches everything. I have an entire pink room lol! I ended up using it to put all my deliveries or random things on and it looks so organized and nice. Eventually I’ll get everything off of it and get my shoes on lol! The quality is great! I seriously love this thing! I’d definitely buy again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Extremely easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my dorm room. It was incredibly easy to assemble. The only thing needed was a hammer, which they included in the package. I’ve had it for about a month now, and it is stable, and works exactly as intended. It is a little bigger than anticipated, but that’s on me for not checking the description.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for kids
reviews.reviewText: Got this for my Daughter's room. She loves it. Was pretty easy to set up, they even included the rubber mallet to make sure poles were tight. Fit perfectly in her closet to keep her shoes organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was missing two of the base parts and have 2 extra bar parts. I give it 4 stars because I was able to make it work, but still.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Decent for price and color
reviews.reviewText: I got this to put shoes and bags on in my room but the size is bigger than I expected and it doesn’t fit into the spot I need it to. I love the color of course it was the main reason for my purchase. My biggest dislike is how wobbly it is. Not much sturdiness, losing major points there. But this will work for now. Not a terrible buy overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This thing is huge! I figured it’d be pretty decent on height but it’s way bigger than expected and I can fit more shoes than I though on it
